                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>write to both him &amp; <persName>George King</persName>. I think<lb/> it will have\n                more weight than any thing<lb/> I can say to them.</p>\n            <p>A great many of the persons you have<lb/> claims against do not appear in the<lb/>\n                city directory so that I cannot find<lb/> them. I will give you a list of such<lb/>\n                as soon as I can find time.</p>\n            <p>With kindest regards to <persName>Mr Cozens</persName><lb/> &amp; the young ladies\n                &amp; best wishes for<lb/> your health &amp; prosperity</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">I remain as ever</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Sincerely Yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">H. S. Hanford</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p37p8v07t/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
